             was indicted for <rs id="t18240603-114-off598" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240603-114-off598" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240603-114-off598" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240603-114-cd599" type="crimeDate">26th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-114-off598 t18240603-114-cd599"></join>, a scarf, value 9 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240603-114-victim974" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Riley
                  <interp inst="t18240603-114-victim974" type="surname" value="Riley"></interp>
